// Section 1: Non-deterministic environment opcodes (exercise + POP)
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
ADDRESS
BALANCE
POP
ORIGIN
POP
CALLER
POP
CALLVALUE
POP
0
CALLDATALOAD
POP
GASPRICE
POP
0
BLOCKHASH
POP
COINBASE
POP
TIMESTAMP
POP
NUMBER
POP
PREVRANDAO
POP
GASLIMIT
POP
CHAINID
POP
SELFBALANCE
POP
BASEFEE
POP
GAS
POP

